Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:48.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}find a way　あたしも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:48.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}find a way　我也一起
